OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,FA nursery worker who raped and abused
OL,7,Fyoung children in his care has been
OL,8,Fjailed for 24 years.
OL,10,FNathan Bennett, 30, preyed on the two
OL,11,Fand three-year-olds at the Partou King
OL,12,FStreet nursery in Bristol.
OL,14,FHe was found guilty by a jury last
OL,15,Fmonth of eight charges including rape,
OL,16,Fsexual assault and assault by
OL,17,Fpenetration, relating to five children.
OL,19,FBennett previously admitted 13 other
OL,20,Fcharges relating to four of the five
OL,21,Fvictims, who were aged two at the time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
