FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,FPassing an extended sentence at
OL,7,FBristol Crown Court of 24 years in
OL,8,Fcustody and a further six years on
OL,9,Flicence, Judge William Hart described
OL,10,FNathan Bennett as an "incorrigible and
OL,11,Fdangerous paedophile".
OL,13,FDuring the trial, jurors heard how
OL,14,Fconcerns were raised by parents and
OL,15,Fstaff about Bennett's behaviour
OL,16,Ftowards the children in his care in
OL,17,FFebruary last year.
OL,19,FThe moment Nathan Bennett is arrested
OL,20,Fby police officers
OL,26,@rD@VOUsD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
