OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,FOn February 26, nursery manager
OL,7,FVictoria Tutton, who was known as
OL,8,FVera, viewed CCTV footage which showed
OL,9,FBennett putting his hands down the
OL,10,Ftrousers of a child and immediately
OL,11,Fsent him home.
OL,13,FAvon and Somerset Police launched an
OL,14,Finvestigation, leading to Bennett's
OL,15,Farrest and later the closure of the
OL,16,Fnursery.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
