OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,FBennett began working at the nursery
OL,7,Fin July 2024 and told staff he was
OL,8,Fautistic, though jurors heard he has
OL,9,Fnever been formally diagnosed with the
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,12,FHe was noted by staff to sit children
OL,13,Fon his lap for lengthy periods of
OL,14,Ftime, wear a pair of trousers with
OL,15,Fholes in the crotch area, and seemed
OL,16,F"territorial" over certain toddlers
OL,17,Fand their parents, the court heard.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
