PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,FNursery practitioner Elizabeth Burton
OL,7,Ftold the court that Bennett had a
OL,8,F"jealous attachment" with five
OL,9,Fchildren and would "take control of
OL,10,Fthem".
OL,12,FDuring the trial, video interviews
OL,13,Fwith two of the children in the case `
OL,14,Freferred to only as Child A and Child
OL,15,FE ` were played to the jury. Child E's
OL,16,Fmother also gave evidence, telling how
OL,17,Fher son had demonstrated how he had
OL,18,Fbeen abused at his nursery.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]qD@TOUrD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
