FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,F"I got him to stop doing it. I asked
OL,7,Fhim when did that happen. He said it
OL,8,Fhappened at nursery," she said.
OL,10,FGiving evidence, Bennett said he was
OL,11,F"emulating" what was done to him as a
OL,12,Fchild and denied having a sexual
OL,13,Fattraction to children.
OL,15,FNathan Bennett is interviewed by
OL,16,Fofficers in custody
OL,18,FDuring sentencing, Judge William Hart
OL,19,Fdescribed Nathan Bennett as 'evil'.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@UO]sD@AOUsD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
