OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,F"These were happy innocent toddlers in
OL,7,Fa secure setting", he said. "The
OL,8,Fchildren we see were not secure. They
OL,9,Fwere at risk.
OL,11,F"You were lurking, and to pollute
OL,12,Ftheir innocence with your own vile
OL,13,Fdesires. You are an incorrigible and
OL,14,Fdangerous paedophile with an
OL,15,Funcontrollable and ungovernable
OL,16,Finterest in male toddlers", he added.
OL,18,F"You prioritised your own sexual
OL,19,Fsatisfaction over the welfare of these
OL,20,Flittle children."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
