OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,F'The worst news the families could
OL,7,Fhave possibly received'
OL,9,FDetective Inspector Lucy Ford from
OL,10,FAvon and Somerset Police described
OL,11,FNathan Bennett as a 'manipulative,
OL,12,Fpredatory paedophile'.
OL,14,F"He is manipulative and he has groomed
OL,15,Fchildren he has committed offences
OL,16,Fagainst. But in doing that, he's
OL,17,Fneeded to groom the adults around him.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,F"My officers had to contact the
OL,7,Fparents of those children who we
OL,8,Fidentified as being victims. It was
OL,9,Fthe most horrendous news they could
OL,10,Fhave possibly received. We have gone
OL,11,Fon to support those family members
OL,12,Fduring the course of the investigation.
OL,14,F"Nathan Bennett chose not to plead
OL,15,Fguilty to the most significant
OL,16,Foffences and has put those families
OL,17,Fand victims through a trial, which has
OL,18,Fbeen challenging and traumatic."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Ford said one of
OL,7,FBennett's victims, who was 3 years
OL,8,Fold, was interviewed by specially-
OL,9,Ftrained officers.
OL,11,F"That is a huge challenge. To get a
OL,12,Fchild of that age to be able to
OL,13,Fcommunicate effectively with officers
OL,14,Fand talk about what's happened to them.
OL,16,F"A child doesn't understand in the
OL,17,Fsame way as an adult does, the
OL,18,Fsignificance of what's happened to
OL,19,Fthem.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,F"He (Bennett) actively pursued a
OL,7,Fcareer in childcare in order to have
OL,8,Fas much opportunity to pursue that as
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,11,F"He's really dangerous. During the
OL,12,Ftrial he didn't acknowledge or admit
OL,13,Fhis guilt, which demonstrates he's got
OL,14,Fvey little insight into the impact of
OL,15,Fhis actions.
OL,17,F"The trauma that (the families) have
OL,18,Fexperienced will last a lifetime", she
OL,19,Fadded.
OL,21,F'Our trust was catastrophically broken'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,FIn a statement issued by Leigh Day
OL,7,Fsolicitors, the families said:
OL,8,F"Today's sentence marks the end of a
OL,9,Fcriminal investigation that has been
OL,10,Fdevastating for families, but it does
OL,11,Fnot begin to repair the harm caused to
OL,12,Fso many children.
OL,14,F"We entrusted our children to Partou
OL,15,FKing Street nursery believing they
OL,16,Fwould be safe, cared for and nurtured.
OL,17,FInstead, that trust was
OL,18,Fcatastrophically broken by someone who
OL,19,Fabused his position in the most
OL,20,Funimaginable way.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,F"Over the months before Bennett's
OL,7,Farrest, a number of parents raised
OL,8,Fconcerns about his behaviour. We know
OL,9,Fconcerns were raised to members of
OL,10,Fstaff ` we believe those warnings and
OL,11,Fcomplaints were not properly followed
OL,12,Fup or escalated.
OL,14,F"Had appropriate action been taken
OL,15,Fsooner, we fear some of the abuse
OL,16,Fchildren suffered may have been
OL,17,Fprevented.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1773666673
OL,3,C'Evil' nursery worker who sexually
OL,4,Cabused children in his care jailed
OL,6,F"Nothing can undo what has happened.
OL,7,FOur focus is now on supporting our
OL,8,Fchildren as they grow, and on seeking
OL,9,Fanswers and accountability from those
OL,10,Fresponsible for ensuring their safety.
OL,12,F"We are grateful to the police and
OL,13,Fprosecutors for bringing Bennett to
OL,14,Fjustice, and to our legal team for now
OL,15,Ftaking up the mantle in investigating
OL,16,Fpotential systemic failings.
OL,18,F"We hope that by speaking out,
OL,19,Fmeaningful changes will be made to
OL,20,Fprotect other children in the future."
OL,26,@nD@AOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/14
